to hash check code at runtime:
[X] 1. add the hash of the text section to the end of the bin
[-] 2. add the necessary linker scripts to expose the hash data and the text to the program
[ ] 3. get the .text section data
[ ] 4. hash the text section
[ ] 5. compare the loaded hash data and the hash for the text section
[ ] 6. finally, return the comparison result